<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 Not Found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background: #3a7bd5;
            background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #3a7bd5, #00d2ff);
        }

        .container {
            background-color: rgba(245, 245, 245, 0.9);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
            transform: translateY(0);
            animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }

        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .container {
                padding: 30px 20px;
                margin: 0 15px;
            }
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
            100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
        }

        .error-icon {
            font-size: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: shake 0.7s ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes shake {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateX(0); }
            10%, 50%, 90% { transform: translateX(-4px); }
            30%, 70% { transform: translateX(4px); }
        }

        h1 {
            color: #5a3f93;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .error-code {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            display: inline-block;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #e74c3c;
            margin: 15px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .error-message {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: -0.2px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #3a7bd5, #00d2ff);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin-top: 15px;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(58, 123, 213, 0.3);
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(58, 123, 213, 0.4);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="error-icon">🙁</div>
        <h1>페이지를 찾을 수 없어요</h1>
        <div class="error-code">404 Not Found</div>
        <div class="error-message">
            요청하신 페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다.<br>
            주소가 올바른지 확인해주세요.
        </div>
        <a href="/" class="cta-button">홈으로 돌아가기</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
